# Comprehensive OpenAI Rules

# General OpenAI Website and API Access
DOMAIN-SUFFIX,openai.com,OpenAI
REGEX,^https?://([a-zA-Z0-9]*\.)?openai\.com,OpenAI

# API Access
DOMAIN,api.openai.com,OpenAI

# GPT-3 and Other Services
DOMAIN,gpt3.openai.com,OpenAI
REGEX,^https?://gpt3\..*\.openai\.com,OpenAI

# Platform and Other Subdomains
DOMAIN,platform.openai.com,OpenAI
REGEX,^https?://([a-zA-Z0-9]*\.)?platform\.openai\.com,OpenAI

# Content and Static Assets
DOMAIN,openaiusercontent.com,OpenAI
REGEX,^https?://.*\.openaiusercontent\.com,OpenAI

# ChatGPT and Specialized Services
DOMAIN,chat.openai.com,OpenAI
REGEX,^https?://chat\..*\.openai\.com,OpenAI

# Cover potential future subdomains or services
REGEX,^https?://([a-zA-Z0-9]*\.)?openai\.org,OpenAI
REGEX,^https?://.*\.openai\.org,OpenAI
